      "content": "but my doctor is always so cautious and just tells me \"don't change anything.\" it's frustrating because everyone says garlic is a natural blood thinner anyway. if i just really ramp up the garlic to like, 3000mg a day and keep the kale smoothies going, wouldn't that naturally keep my blood thin enough to avoid a clot without the warfarin side effects? it just seems like a much more natural way to handle it.",
